        "timestamp": "2019-05-15 17:53:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nSteve, I was thinking that we should keep the source-processor-db name for Dublin and change it to source-primary-db in El Alto. For vDNS testing all our data dictionary has the source-processor-db.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "7e8e94259718f5d0723166c2d281bb5f8062aff3",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 4567,
          "name": "Yuriy Malakov",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "yuriy.malakov@att.com",
          "username": "ym9479"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-15 17:57:48.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThe initial thought was that we would consolidate the source db reference in resource mapping to be just primary-db and add aai reference. \n\nresourceSourceMappings=processor-db=source-primary-db,primary-db=source-primary-db,",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
