        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-15 18:28:15.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi Yuriy,\n\nThis exactly what I have done. I changed source-processor-db to source-primary-db and add AAI ref.\n\nLet's discuss on that to finalize this.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
