        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-15 19:13:11.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nYuriy,\n\nas we just discuss, these are the two things to finalize this bug:\n1. Keep only one source type: source-processor-db\n2. Keep two sources: processor-db and primary-db\n\nI apply the change now.",
